modules.description: This module parses and handles multipart/form-data streams using both streaming and in-memory approaches. It provides `stream` to process multipart data incrementally, returning a promise and a stream of part contents, and `save_part` to persist individual parts to files. The non-streaming functions `of_stream_to_list` and `of_stream_to_tree` collect all parts into memory, suitable for small payloads, with the latter assembling a full in-memory tree structure.
